qooxdoo-archetype-gui
=====================

The qooxdoo-archetype-gui is a maven archetype to create a qooxdoo application within a maven project.

******************************************************************
IMPORTANT: this artifact is deployed on a maven repository:

To start a new qooxdoo-maven project:
TODO
******************************************************************

The following are for developper that want to install the artifact into their local repository.

1) Install archetype in local repo, reindex catalog

$ git clone git://github.com/salmon-charles/qooxdoo-archetype-gui.git
$ cd qooxdoo-archetype-gui
$ mvn clean install
$ mvn archetype:crawl

2) Create a new mvn-qooxdoo project
$ cd /tmp
$ mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=org.charless -DartifactId=appname -Dversion=0.1-SNAPSHOT -DarchetypeGroupId=org.qooxdoo.archetypes -DarchetypeArtifactId=qooxdoo-archetype-gui -DarchetypeVersion=1.4   -Dpackage=appname
$ cd appname
$ mvn clean compile

3) Test
Open a browser and go to file:///tmp/appname/target/qooxdoo/qxapp/build/index.html





